<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>v67 실제 제작 품질 개선 리포트</title>
<style>
body{font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",sans-serif;background:#f5f7fb;color:#172033;margin:0;padding:28px;}
.wrap{max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;}
.hero{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#111827,#2563eb,#06b6d4);color:white;border-radius:28px;padding:28px 32px;box-shadow:0 18px 42px rgba(15,23,42,.20);}
.card{background:white;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:22px;padding:20px;margin-top:18px;box-shadow:0 10px 28px rgba(15,23,42,.06);}
.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:16px;}
.preview{background:white;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:18px;padding:12px;text-align:center;}
.preview img{max-width:220px;border-radius:18px;background:white;}
.score{font-size:30px;font-weight:800;color:#2563eb;}
.badge{display:inline-block;background:#e0f2fe;color:#075985;border-radius:999px;padding:5px 10px;margin:3px;font-weight:700;}
pre{white-space:pre-wrap;background:#0f172a;color:#e5e7eb;border-radius:16px;padding:16px;overflow:auto;}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
  <div class="hero">
    <h1>v67 실제 제작 품질 개선 리포트</h1>
    <p>정지형 → 움직이는형 미리보기 · 영상 참고형 카카오 품질 방향 · 선택 제안 실제 반영</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>프로젝트</h2>
    <p><b>{{ project_name }}</b></p>
    <p>{{ concept_text }}</p>
    <p>스타일: <b>{{ selected_style }}</b></p>
    {% for item in selected_suggestions %}
      <span class="badge">{{ item }}</span>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>바로 보이는 결과</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="preview">
        <h3>정지형 PNG</h3>
        <img src="data:image/png;base64,{{ static_png_b64 }}">
      </div>
      <div class="preview">
        <h3>대표 움직이는 GIF</h3>
        <img src="data:image/gif;base64,{{ animated_gif_b64 }}">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>모션 후보</h2>
    <div class="grid">
    {% for item in motion_gifs %}
      <div class="preview">
        <h3>{{ item.label }}</h3>
        <img src="data:image/gif;base64,{{ item.b64 }}">
        <p>{{ item.phrase }} · {{ item.motion }}</p>
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>품질 점수</h2>
    <div class="grid">
    {% for k, v in quality_scores.items() %}
      <div><div class="score">{{ v }}</div><div>{{ k }}</div></div>
    {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>영상 기준 반영</h2>
    <pre>{{ video_reference_summary_json }}</pre>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>온라인 기준 반영</h2>
    <pre>{{ online_reference_basis_json }}</pre>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>identity lock</h2>
    <pre>{{ identity_lock_json }}</pre>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>안전 메모</h2>
    <ul>
    {% for note in safety_notes %}
      <li>{{ note }}</li>
    {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>